title="Frobenius morphism">Frobenius morphism</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\phi (x)=x^{p}]]></fr:tex> gives us
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\phi _{r}(x)=x^{p^{r}}=\underbrace {\phi \circ \cdots \circ \phi }_{r\text { times}}.]]></fr:tex>
Hence
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\langle \phi \rangle =\mathop {\textrm {Aut}}\nolimits (\Bbbk  / \mathbb {F}),]]></fr:tex>
which is a finite cycle group of order <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>

 
   
